{"tid":2443210,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"講開《先生貴姓》，仲有無巴絲記得當年有套劇叫《衝上人間》","createTime":"2021-03-12T02:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:16:17.000Z","uid":297629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"71400dd4ac568c2a58b7c508cfae1f74d00863db","tid":2443210,"uid":297629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T02:08:45.000Z","msg":"仲記得當年因為有小朋友模仿出左事，被迫縮短套劇，但當年來講套劇係幾創新好睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://1327020374.rsc.cdn77.org/update/CA/Large/ASmilingGhostStory_Large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1327020374.rsc.cdn77.org%2Fupdate%2FCA%2FLarge%2FASmilingGhostStory_Large.jpg&h=555b9155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林家宜（張可頤飾）為人開朗活潑，常愛助人，深得人喜愛。但一次意外，家宜因救人竟觸電死亡，雖得在場的古德明（郭晉安飾）即時搶救及施以人工呼吸，惜仍返魂無術。家宜到陰間得優先投胎，好奇下翻查名冊，竟發現來世的父母是其表姐文少英（陳法蓉飾）和方志龍（張家輝飾）。但少英與志龍卻是鬥氣冤家，為撮合二人，家宜不惜向鬼褓姆周小波（林曉峰飾）及死前曾和她通了氣的德明求助。<br />\n志龍和少英在德明及家宜暗中安排下，終化敵為愛，走進教堂，更成功創業，生意興隆。而德明跟家宜相處日久，竟動了真情。二人相戀卻被德明拍拖多年的女友趙淑美（袁彩雲飾）揭發，一怒下設計欲把家宜驅走&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25A1%259D%25E4%25B8%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2596%2593&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=10c76421\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%BA%E9%96%93</a>"},{"pid":"0bc08b4a90a5b6e452a7f061f4651c82e1016dcd","tid":2443210,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T03:23:22.000Z","msg":"死得好唔抵"},{"pid":"1282a64f1a5bdc06860e75ffc212c13919dad201","tid":2443210,"uid":297629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"原來無人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c14b31433051c3c0d7b66205476ca7c165c987","tid":2443210,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1282a64f1a5bdc06860e75ffc212c13919dad201","tid":2443210,"uid":297629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T04:06:53.000Z","msg":"原來無人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"好似08年重播睇過<br />\n最記得係化骨龍啲演技好正"},{"pid":"0746b38dce3499237eea75edb402a57baacdb3b1","tid":2443210,"uid":190576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:38:34.000Z","msg":"張家輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好好笑"},{"pid":"292da5f3a235df8bac2e1d8e6aca5bc030a15a00","tid":2443210,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K7xjhFuKGv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK7xjhFuKGv4&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=fac7b7a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K7xjhFuKGv4</a>"},{"pid":"c75004ed8f52163e61532d9474cecddf2c38f088","tid":2443210,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:13:15.000Z","msg":"完全無印象"},{"pid":"18b3e1bb43cd9fc77ee90e6692c8b1b09465ff9f","tid":2443210,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:14:03.000Z","msg":"飛越十八層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da16952d825769830020bc57b90beda99298a51","tid":2443210,"uid":20286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"記得個名<br />\n但套野無乜印象<br />\n<br />\nDiana印象深啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}